0.HMLE - HanMLE (Multi-Line Edit) Control

HMLE를 사용하려면 HMLE.h와 HMLE.a(HMLE.lib)를 각각 include/link 시켜야 함.

 이 문서에 언급되지 않은 윈도우 스타일,메시지,통지 메시지(Notification msg)등은
정상적으로 작동한다고 볼 수 없음.이 문서에 언급된 것들은 불완전하지만,
그런대로 사용은 가능함.


1.Window Class : WC_HMLE ("HanMLE")

	BOOL RegisterHanMLEControl(HAB hab);

2.Window Styles :

	HMLS_BORDER
	HMLS_VSCROLL
	HMLS_READONLY
	HMLS_IGNORETAB
	HMLS_STATUSNOTIFY
	HMLS_NOAUTOCREATEHIA
	HMLS_ACCEPTFILEDROP

3.Window Messages :

	HMLM_NEWDOC
	HMLM_SETIMPORTEXPORT
	HMLM_QUERYIMPORTEXPORT
	HMLM_IMPORT
	HMLM_EXPORT
	HMLM_QUERYTEXTLENGTH
	HMLM_QUERYFORMATTEXTLENGTH
	HMLM_QUERYSELTEXT
	HMLM_SETEOLTYPE
	HMLM_QUERYEOLTYPE
	HMLM_SETTEXTFORMAT
	HMLM_QUERYTEXTFORMAT
	HMLM_SETHANTYPE
	HMLM_QUERYHANTYPE
	HMLM_SETCHANGED
	HMLM_QUERYCHANGED
	HMLM_SETREADONLY
	HMLM_QUERYREADONLY
	HMLM_SETSEL
	HMLM_QUERYSEL
	HMLM_SETFIRSTCHAR
	HMLM_QUERYFIRSTCHAR
	HMLM_SETTABSTOP
	HMLM_QUERYTABSTOP
	HMLM_SETTEXTCOLOR
	HMLM_QUERYTEXTCOLOR
	HMLM_SETBACKCOLOR
	HMLM_QUERYBACKCOLOR
	HMLM_SETSELTEXTCOLOR
	HMLM_QUERYSELTEXTCOLOR
	HMLM_SETSELBACKCOLOR
	HMLM_QUERYSELBACKCOLOR
	HMLM_COPY
	HMLM_CUT
	HMLM_PASTE
	HMLM_CLEAR
	HMLM_INSERT
	HMLM_DELETE
	HMLM_REFRESH
	HMLM_REFRESHSCROLLBAR
	HMLM_QUERYHIA
	HMLM_SETHIA
	HMLM_SEARCH

  1) HMLM_NEWDOC :
  2) HMLM_SETEOLTYPE :

	Export(Clipboard export 포함)시 사용할 텍스트의 형식을 설정
	(HMLE내부적으로는 항상 LF사용)

	mp1 : 텍스트 형식

		HMLE_EOL_CRLF
		HMLE_EOL_LF

  3) HMLM_QUERYEOLTYPE

  4) HMLM_SETHANTYPE

	Export/Import(Clipboard export/import 포함)시 사용할
	한글코드의 형식을 설정.(HMLE 내부적으로는 항상 상용조합형 사용)

	mp1 : 한글 코드

		HMLE_HAN_KS
		HMLE_HAN_SY

  5) HMLM_QUERYHANTYPE

  6) HMLM_SETHIA

	HIA에 등록.(HEF의 HEM_SETHIA 설명 참조)

  7) HMLM_QUERYHIA


4.Window Notification Messages (WM_CONTROL Messages) :

	HMLN_SETFOCUS
	HMLN_KILLFOCUS
	HMLN_CHANGED
	HMLN_BEGINSELECTION
	HMLN_ENDSELECTION


5.Window Control Data Structure :

typedef struct
{
	USHORT cb;
	ULONG eol_type;
	ULONG han_type;
	ULONG maxLineSize;
	HWND hwndHIA;
} HMLECTLDATA, *PHMLECTLDATA;